Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra, open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's the day I'm going to\Ntake you in for a check up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling you that it's\Npointless to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think\NI'm coming here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody called you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You stubborn, narrow-minded woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk, you quack doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been to a doctor\Nsince I was born, but I'm still healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!\NBad news–!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Schumann!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fink, the drunkard was hit\Nby a car on the highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So is he still conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who brought him in\Nis treating him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that some man who happened\Nto be passing by is examining him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.49,0:01:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You were visiting homes,\Nso that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You let him treat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I tried to stop him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but he said that he needed to\Napply first aid
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,because there was a chance that\Nthe patient would choke...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?\NHe left without saying his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...he wrote something\Non the medical chart...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"The patient has no money."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"He kept repeating not to\Ntake him to a doctor."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please take this money\Nas his doctor's fee"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does he think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he look like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an Asian man with a boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, what about Fink's treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep him in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...the man only\Napplied first aid...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not first aid...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,His treatment was complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really a problem if you follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go to school.\NYou can't make any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who\Ncame to my clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and did unnecessary things,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that Fink is a broke alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no intention of\Ncharging him for treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably some elite\Nfrom a first-rate hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to show some compassion\Nwhile on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.\N– Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Dieter!\N– Are you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N– Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to what I have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fink got into a hit-and-run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fink, the drunkard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking for witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... That's a tough task.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dr. Schumann.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Fink's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,His life's not in danger. I'm more\Nworried about his alcoholism.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,An underclassman from college.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's visiting this village\Nduring his vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Chan? Have we met somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He treated Fink for me\Nwhile I was visiting homes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside, where do you think I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At Petra's house...\Nyour mother, Heinz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her to come to the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We may need to treat her\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That stubborn woman\Nwon't listen to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act as if it's not your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Mom won't die that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha–?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, she raised me this far.\NI don't think she has any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra's life has just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That was for saving Fink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He would have died if it wasn't\Nfor your swift treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You turned so pale\Nwhen you saw the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,at least it's obvious that you're not\Nan elite doctor from a first-rate hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\NI don't know how to repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Repay me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then help me out a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your splint is misaligned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This may hurt a bit,\Nbut please be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it should be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can probably take it off\Nafter two more weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I made some good cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NYou're hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drink with you all night\Nonce you've healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Progress is good. Five days\Nand you can go back to the fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad, Schone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, take some potatoes.\NThis year's crop is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I'll come with a truck\Nand take a whole mountain of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NMy specialty is internal medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I do what I can outside my specialty...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But things don't go very well\Nwhen I'm by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's nothing here,\Nbut it's a peaceful village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're loved by the people here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And you really love them too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Love, huh?\NI lost feelings like that a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come with me\Nto just one more house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are persistent, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll keep coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be the same no matter\Nhow many times you come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You quack doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the mother\Nof that police officer earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She fell sick while farming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to get her to my clinic,\Nbut on the way there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,she said that she's fine\Nand went back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's worrisome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:08:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I try to reason with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll probably be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still loitering there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can loiter wherever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. She'll never come out\Nif you yell like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get you out. I'm not going\Nto lose my reason for living!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I just meant that I wouldn't\Nhave anyone to fight with anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Also, I wouldn't be able to eat\Nher goulash anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, your face is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?! You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up, Mrs. Petra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? A different doctor now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless to talk to\Nthat stubborn woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you hate doctors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Well, humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They fiddle around\Nwith peoples' bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and think that they're gods\Nor something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,God, huh? Sometimes I think that\Nit would be great if we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We try our best, but no matter what,\Nwe make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish that I could heal people\Nperfectly like God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always trembling inside\Nwhenever I see my patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. At least let me see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This smell... You're making goulash,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? Do you like goulash?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But it seems that Dr. Schumann\Nespecially loves your goulash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's news to me. He always eats it\Nwithout a word whenever I make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...\NMy shoulders are stiff,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but it looks like\NI have to prepare dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stiff shoulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Petra, can you put\Nyour chin to your chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Ow ow ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Four fingers fit...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Some kind of prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No...nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably...\Na subarachnoid hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the fax of the arrest warrant\Nfor the murder suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Make copies of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your mom okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that she collapsed\Nthree days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's all right. She wouldn't die\Neven if you killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 72 hours\Nsince the first stroke...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make it.\NWe've got to operate immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if a helicopter\Ncan make it if we call for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N– Please,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,perform the operation\Nif you can... If not...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be my fault again for\Nlosing another person I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure that it's Kenzo Tenma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N– All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He might not have gone far!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Set up a barrier along the highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be great if we catch him, Heinz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, emergency deployment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! I can get a promotion\Nif things go well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heinz, you have a call!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! This is Heinz...\NOh, hello, Nurse...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom collapsed again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had forced her to\Nget a check up at a national hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,after the first stroke...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one\NI can count on, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as I thought. It's an aneurysm\Nof the middle cerebral artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!\NWe don't have a surgical microscope
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,or a craniotome here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can try open surgery as long as\NI have an aneurysm clip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too difficult even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She may not live the next time\Nthe cranial aneurysm ruptures...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault that\Nthis happened again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dr. Schumann?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You single-handedly took care of\Nthe patients of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened\Nin the past, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to try our best\Nfor the patient before us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all we can do as doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, boy, is Dr. Schumann inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's operating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Operating on my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They're operating at this clinic\Nrather than taking her
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to a hospital in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Tenma is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How's her blood pressure and pulse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure 126/84.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pulse 88.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing... He opened her head\Nso fast with just a wire saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even have a craniotome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, we are\Noperating on your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with that gun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your hands, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the middle of an operation!\NAre you trying to kill your mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:15:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma is a murder suspect\Nthat's been on the run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed a man in Heidelberg.\NHe's even suspected of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the serial killing of\Nmiddle-aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought that I'd find him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to Mom.\NShe saw an opportunity for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, raise your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a sterile operating room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're bringing in germs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother could die\Nfrom meningitis if you spread it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then quickly stop the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want your mom to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother has\Na subarachnoid hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She first collapsed three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't deal with it now\Nit'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you've got a hostage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're planning to use my mom\Nas a hostage and run away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aneurysm clip and forceps...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Aneurysm clip and forceps!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Petra is your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But what have you done for her\Nin the past five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you visited her even once\Nsince you left the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you ever done\Nfor your mother
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,after she raised you this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, people who are dear to us\Nwill pass away some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the taste of\Nyour mother's goulash?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, Petra makes portions\Nfor you out of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I eat what's left over. It's delicious!\NThat taste is superb!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is desperately fighting\Nto save your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to eat that goulash again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Tenma is here, so it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure 140/86. Pulse 82.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Vital signs are stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pionier, you should get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right. Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, you get some rest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You performed a difficult operation\Nthat lasted three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay alert and watch her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So that you can propose to Mrs. Petra\Nwhen she gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "propose"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep.\NNot until I take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides that, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to propose\Nto my mom, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be foolish! Don't be foolish...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:18:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...not someone who can\Npropose to anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was\Nat the university hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I never cared about talking\Nto my patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I only thought of how I could\Nraise my position in the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I got into the director's faction\Nand wrote papers for the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I even married the director's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I pushed forward along\Nthe path of success even after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I never paid any attention to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If I was a real doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have noticed\Nwhen I had seen her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,For a long time,\Nmy wife had symptoms
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,which mimicked the common cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have noticed\Nif I were watching closely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was liver failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When she took her last breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You finally... paid attention to me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no right to love anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been paying attention\Nto the people of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra was saved because\Nyou were paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still plan on taking\Nthis man away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the man who struggled\Nto save your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still think he's a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Heinz!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Heinz. Get me the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, I'm sorry. I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The man I saw wasn't Tenma.\NHe was Dr. Chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I made the mistake\Nbecause he was Asian...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor of the national hospital\Nwas sure surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably never thought that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,he would see such amazing treatment\Nfrom a clinic in the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to let\Nthat young doctor go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to make him\Nsomething to eat, but he went off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go, this village is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Schumann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter, you like it here, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.\NThis village may be good for Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only for Dieter. This village\Ncan protect you from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the people here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This village needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, I'm going with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay here,\Nyou can save the lives
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of countless people in this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Save countless lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I...have to kill a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Tenma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can do\Nsuch a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You try so desperately to save\Npeoples' lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma's going no matter\Nwhat you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma won't lose his way\Nif you're with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch Tenma carefully.
